metadata.name: Navigating Reality
metadata.description:
Reality can be a dark place for a lot of people, the  
world is filled with hate and abuse, terrible  
people and systems, pain and suffering. And  
we are forced to navigate through it because  
we are alive. We push forward through the  
dark waters in search of something we are not  
sure of and at any moment without notice the  
darkness might consume us.  
For a lot of people to be alive is to just be  
swimming through this dark place alone and  
isolated from the rest of the world searching  
for peace and themselves.

I hope you find the bubbles of light in the overwhelming darkness of existence.
